data.description: Priced to sell! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home sits on a corner lot. It features an open concept, new roof, and updated bathrooms. This property has a large fenced-in yard with a covered patio and a large detached shed. The refrigerator,  washer, and dryer stay. This property is in an XFlood zone and is move in ready! Motivated seller will offer some closing cost help and up to $700 towards a home warranty.  Make this your home or an investment property. Measurements are approximate and not guaranteed
